298
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:21,820
You can tell me.

299
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:24,400
I can bring you what you like next time.

300
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:25,480
Actually,

301
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:27,560
I haven't eaten out much.

302
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,620
My mom always cooks for me.

303
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,540
Your mom is really nice to you.

304
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:35,130
Let's go.

305
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:38,900
Where is this from?

306
00:23:39,120 --> 00:23:40,650
I think it's called Li Dafu.

307
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:51,240
Regarding the re-firing of ancient kilns,

308
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:52,920
