323
00:24:16,840 --> 00:24:18,360
What is its significance?

324
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,800
To create a tourist attraction.

325
00:24:21,080 --> 00:24:22,720
You have a head for business.

326
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,800
Re-firing is a living inheritance.

327
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:27,200
Jingdezhen must pass on this kiln fire.

328
00:24:28,320 --> 00:24:29,380
That is one reason.

329
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:32,130
This afternoon,

330
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:36,240
I will take the students to visit Weijiayao.

331
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:38,560
We will have a field study there.

332
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,280
Going to Weijiayao this afternoon.

333
00:24:41,280 --> 00:24:43,140
Does it mean we can go for a picnic?

334
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:44,080
These ancient kilns

335
