340
00:24:52,280 --> 00:24:54,440
We need to combine learning and entertainment.

341
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,100
Lin Yuexin.

342
00:24:55,360 --> 00:24:56,840
Let's have lunch together.

343
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:58,040
We will go to the convenience store later

344
00:24:58,040 --> 00:24:59,360
