345
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:00,760
See what you want to buy.

346
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:01,440
It's rare for you to be so thoughtful.

347
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:02,240
Is your stomach feeling better?

348
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:02,960
Of course.

349
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:05,600
Is Weijiayao near Hanxi Village?

350
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:06,960
I heard it's very beautiful there,

351
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,490
