357
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:20,130
You should have told me.

358
00:25:20,280 --> 00:25:20,960
What?

359
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:23,240
Your thoughts and feelings,

360
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:24,540
